WEBVTT

00:00.445 --> 00:02.186
Previously on,<i> The Arrangement...</i>

00:02.187 --> 00:03.787
This role will elevate you,

00:03.856 --> 00:05.088
but we have to fight for it.

00:05.157 --> 00:08.025
June, your story needs to be told by women.

00:08.093 --> 00:09.669
I hope you make a strong bid.

00:09.670 --> 00:11.216
I'm introducing something new.

00:11.217 --> 00:13.617
It's called Vita, it's
IHM's life extension program.

00:14.147 --> 00:16.219
Aaron! Julie!

00:16.457 --> 00:17.656
<i>Aaron and Julie are gone.</i>

00:17.724 --> 00:19.357
Shit, Terence.

00:19.426 --> 00:21.293
I swear to you, I didn't tell him anything.

00:21.361 --> 00:23.762
That is so pathetic that
I would actually think

00:23.831 --> 00:25.197
that you would choose me over him.

00:25.265 --> 00:26.932
We're getting married tomorrow!

00:27.000 --> 00:28.443
We're gonna have to figure
out what to do about her.

00:28.635 --> 00:29.935
What did you have in mind?

00:30.003 --> 00:31.919
I think we're gonna need
a more permanent solution.

00:32.326 --> 00:34.292
It's over. Terence has them.

00:34.361 --> 00:36.161
What? No, Kyle wouldn't let that happen.

00:36.230 --> 00:37.896
Yeah, who knows what Kyle would do.

00:37.965 --> 00:39.264
<i>Where are you right now?</i>

